    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s been super reliable for all my daily trips. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-cared for, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for a new owner to get behind the wheel. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
