    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This unit features independent throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, while the chassis remains composed thanks to Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a factory carbon fiber roof for a lower center of gravity. Preventative maintenance is up to date, specifically addressing rod bearings and throttle actuators. The suspension bushings and subframe mounts are firm, providing excellent lateral stability. While the finish shows light patina from spirited use, the powertrain and drivetrain harmonics are exceptional. A true driver\u2019s specification.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
