      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car that\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for weekend getaways or just getting around town comfortably! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s looking for a new owner who will enjoy it as much as I have. It runs smooth and is ready to hit the road today\u2014come take it for a spin!",
