    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s M-Division engineering, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, complemented by a factory-spec limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Recent service includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the structural integrity matches its high-revving performance. With precise steering rack feedback and a crisp Getrag gearbox, this vehicle offers a tactile, analog driving experience that remains the benchmark for the segment.",
